{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"36641-the-three-little-kittens","title":"The Three Little Kittens","description":"Three little kittens are afraid of the neighbourhood dog. He really wants to play with them, but whenever they see him they run away! Why do you think they are so scared of him?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Magdalena  Cooper"],"illustrators":["Youm Kosal"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/36641-the-three-little-kittens"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101318/size3/a997546bf81a177c22005e6474cb2c66.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101318/size6/a997546bf81a177c22005e6474cb2c66.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69716/size6/67fc4ae820996a81ed297a035756af36.jpg","text":"One day three little kittens meet a big dog.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69717/size6/8b76b882c071045c557571ec4661c990.jpg","text":"The kittens are scared of the dog.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69718/size6/1f9debea76b9c71f6f98e574a7d6966b.jpg","text":"The little kittens run...","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69719/size6/08185ceaf85ab4ae2a515524f7b83037.jpg","text":"...and the dog follows them.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69720/size6/9afb6ff01db277c4ff0ca799f6bbfa93.jpg